'''比德加纳爆炸事件'''是一件發生在2011年11月12日[[伊朗|伊朗]]當地時間13:30，在莫達勒斯飛彈基地的大爆炸案件<ref name=mysterious>[http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/mysterious-explosions-pose-dilemma-for-iranian-leaders/2011/11/23/gIQA8IsSvN_story.html Mysterious explosions pose dilemma for Iranian leaders] {{Webarchive|url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20111125223735/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/mysterious-explosions-pose-dilemma-for-iranian-leaders/2011/11/23/gIQA8IsSvN_story.html |date=2011-11-25 }}. washingtonpost.com . 23 November 2011</ref>，17名[[伊朗革命卫队|伊朗革命卫队]]人員殉難<ref>[http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/courts-law/iran-exile-group-claims-blast-near-tehran-hit-closely-guarded-missile-base/2011/11/12/gIQArKv4FN_story.html Iran exile group claims blast near Tehran hit closely guarded missile base] {{Wayback|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/courts-law/iran-exile-group-claims-blast-near-tehran-hit-closely-guarded-missile-base/2011/11/12/gIQArKv4FN_story.html |date=20111113002050 }}. ''The Washington Post''. 13 November 2011.</ref>，包括被形容為「伊朗飛彈計劃重要人物」哈桑·德黑兰尼·穆加达姆少將<ref name=expert>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/nov/14/iran-explosion-missile-expert Iranian missile expert killed in explosion] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/nov/14/iran-explosion-missile-expert |date=20130604075217 }} ''The Guardian'', 13 November 2011</ref>。

伊朗革命卫队駐軍在[[沙赫黎亚|沙赫黎亚]]附近的一條村落，在首都[[德黑蘭|德黑蘭]]以東約48公里。[[卡拉季|卡拉季]]居民聽到爆炸聲和附近建築物玻璃碎裂<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/persian/iran/2011/11/111112_ka_tehran_explosion.shtml |title=سپاه پاسداران:انفجار مربوط به یک زاغه مهمات بود |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |date=12 November 2011 |work= |publisher=bbc |accessdate=12 November 2011 |archive-date=2015-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521034149/http://www.bbc.co.uk/persian/iran/2011/11/111112_ka_tehran_explosion.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。初步報告顯示爆炸發生在[[壓縮天然氣|壓縮天然氣]]站<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mehrnews.com/fa/NewsDetail.aspx?NewsID=1458098 |title=صدای مهیب در تهران و کرج |date=12 November 2011 |work= |publisher=خبرگزاری مهر |accessdate=12 November 2011 |archive-date=2012-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120226085108/http://www.mehrnews.com/fa/newsdetail.aspx?NewsID=1458098 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，但後來被否認<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mehrnews.com/fa/NewsDetail.aspx?NewsID=1458126 |title=انفجار جایگاه CNG در تهران و البرز صحت ندارد |date=12 November 2011 |work= |publisher=خبرگزاری مهر |accessdate=12 November 2011 |archive-date=2012-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213040711/http://www.mehrnews.com/fa/NewsDetail.aspx?NewsID=1458126 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。伊朗革命卫队官方指該爆炸發生時，軍方人員正在運送軍需品<ref name=expert/>。縱使專家指出自2010年起煉油廠和燃气管道爆炸事件以五倍猛增，官方仍否認任何由外國策劃爆炸案的可能性<ref name=mysterious/> 。

根據[[CNN|CNN]]報導，[[五角大廈|五角大廈]]高官指出，[[美國政府|美國政府]]相信，該爆炸案是純粹一場意外，是注合[[揮發性|揮發性]]燃料不慎，而引致爆炸<ref>{{cite news |title=About that Iran explosion... |first=Barbara |last=Starr |url=http://security.blogs.cnn.com/2011/11/17/about-that-iran-explosion/ |newspaper=CNN.com |date=17 November 2011 |accessdate=28 November 2011 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325212629/https://security.blogs.cnn.com/2011/11/17/about-that-iran-explosion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。商用人造衛星在11月22日拍攝的圖像顯示該基地受到嚴重損壞，部份建築物更完全摧毀<ref>{{cite web |url=http://isis-online.org/isis-reports/detail/satellite-image-showing-damage-from-november-12-2011-blast-at-military-base/ |title=Satellite Image Showing Damage from November 12, 2011 Blast at Military Base in Iran |last1=Brannan |first1=Paul |last2= |first2= |date=17 November 2011 |work= |publisher=Institute for Science and International Security |accessdate=28 November 2011 |archive-date=2021-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202110845/https://isis-online.org/isis-reports/detail/satellite-image-showing-damage-from-november-12-2011-blast-at-military-base/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==以色列破壞可能==
消息來源指出，[[幕後黑手|幕後黑手]]可能是[[以色列情報特務局|以色列情報特務局]]（俗稱摩薩德），根據《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代雜誌]]》引述一名不透露姓名的官員表示，該爆炸事件是並非一場意外<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2099376,00.html |title=Was Israel Behind a Deadly Explosion at an Iranian Missile Base? |access-date=2014-05-22 |archive-date=2011-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111114011528/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2099376,00.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，當[[以色列國防部|以色列國防部]]部長[[埃胡德·巴拉克|埃胡德·巴拉克]]被問及該事件是否是意外時，他回答「也許有可能」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jpost.com/IranianThreat/News/Article.aspx?id=245467 |title=Barak hopes there will be more explosions in Iran |access-date=2014-05-22 |archive-date=2012-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120117175214/http://www.jpost.com/IranianThreat/News/Article.aspx?id=245467 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

